flowchart TD
    O[Load coordinates and current cover] --> L[LiLuMaxVary or another vary family]
    L --> K[Candidate codes]
    K --> C[Calculate region / MRR]
    C --> Q{Valid nonempty result?}
    Q -- certified empty --> L
    Q -- internal failure --> D[Debug; never cache as empty]
    Q -- yes --> A[Add stable or valid triple to cover data]
    A --> H[Find and inspect remaining holes]
    H --> T{Need a different construction?}
    T -- triples --> R[Tokarsky triples workflow]
    T -- patterned family --> P[LiPattern / iterate-to-limit]
    T -- hard local case --> M[Manual Vary plus Calculate]
    T -- continue batch --> L
    R --> A
    P --> C
    M --> C
